                <note rend="inline" type="source">724.3415/525: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                        Chargé in Argentina</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">White</hi>
                    </persName>)<note n="27" xml:id="d702fn27">The same, <hi rend="italic">mutatis
                            mutandis</hi>, on the same date to the Ambassador in Brazil as telegram
                        No. 15.</note>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1929-05-11T18:00:00-04:00"
                            >May 11, 1929—6 p.m.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>37. Formal action is to be taken May 13 by the Commission of Inquiry and
                    Conciliation, Bolivia and Paraguay, with regard to the repatriation of
                    prisoners. The plan will probably call for the services of the Military Attaché
                    at your mission. Please ask him to be ready.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Stimson</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
